+- **Modified**: [static/index.html](file:///d:/antigravity_sandbox/DealFinderAmazonPy/static/index.html)
+- **Modified**: [static/style.css](file:///d:/antigravity_sandbox/DealFinderAmazonPy/static/style.css)
